title: Cam'ron Interview and More
itunes:title: Cam'ron Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had Kill Cam in the building, where the topic of discussion was the beef between him and Mase, even though if you ask Cam'ron he did not make a diss track, he was just "telling stories on real life situations". Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Laura Ingraham after she was trying to demonize Kendrick and Jay-Z lyrics. Moreover, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
